Paper: hep-th/9711174

Date: 1997-11-24

Title: The U(1) and Strong CP Problem From the Loop Formulation Perspective

Authors: H. Fort and R. Gambini (IFFC, Montevideo, Uruguay)

Comments: 4 pages, revtex

We show how the gauge invariant formulation of QCD in terms of loops is freefrom a hidden $\theta$ parameter and offers an alternative way to solve the$U(1)_A$ puzzle.